channel.description:
[IMG]http://i576.photobucket.com/albums/ss201/amstaf_album/rspsoft.jpg[/img] Welcome to RSPSOFT v1.1
[U][B]RSPSOFT is based on final devolution Released By KillMess.[/B][/U]
[u][b]Features[/b][/u]
[u][b]#: PVP following [/b][/u] [B]This includes, Range, Melee[/B]
[u][b]#: Teleporting[/b][/u] [B]You can teleport with Modern/Ancients and Runes require to use the teleports.[/B]
[u][b]#: Perfect Combat Switch from Ice Blitz to DDS[/b][/u]
[b][u]Barrows Effect[/u][/b]
[B]Dharok Hits higher while it's have Lower HP, guthan does drain heal from the victim. [/B]
[u][b]#: Prayer[/b][/u]
[B]All prayer from the old school works.[/B]
[u][b]Barrows[/b][/u] [B]Good old barrows, Spade Dig the monstor gets mad and attacking you.[/B]
There is alot more.
[u][b]Skills[/b][/u]
[U]Farming Basic version though. Firemaking. Theiving.[/U]
Todo List. [QUOTE] New minigame hpefully pest controle. [s]Fixing the easy way of xlog[/s] - DONE Modern/Ancient AutoCast. Adding More Skills such as, Woodocutting, Mining, smithing, Flehtning, Slayer, Crafting. [s]Fixing The Trading[/s]- DONE [s]Dark Bow[/s] - DONE [s]Barrows[/s] - DONE [/QUOTE]
[U][B]i will hopefully add more.[/B][/U]
